            <p>Book 15 minutes with our team — we will show how theStacc replaces 3–4 tools at a fraction of the stack cost.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book demo <span>→</span></a>
